<bioghist altrender="history" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
<head>Historical Note</head>
<p>
The town of Waterbury was incorporated in May 1686. The city of Waterbury was incorporated in 1853. The town and city consolidated in 1902. The town is located in New Haven County.
</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
<head>Scope and Content</head>
<p>
The air raid shelter survey includes information on the classification of buildings as air raid shelters and building survey forms used to collect construction data on individual buildings. 
</p>
</scopecontent>

<arrangement encodinganalog="351$b" id="a5">
<head>Arrangement</head>
<p>
The building survey forms were sorted by street and each form assigned a sequential number. They are arranged as follows: buildings posted as air raid shelters, buildings determined to be unsuitable, and the remaining forms by street then by number.
</p>
</arrangement>

<relatedmaterial encodinganalog="544 1" id="a6">
<head>Related Material</head>
<p>None.</p>
</relatedmaterial>

